===選角===
[[File:Russell_Tovey.jpg|thumb]]在本集中出演亨利·奈特一角。]]
《巴斯克維爾獵犬》的主角除福爾摩斯和華生外，還有亨利·奈特。劇組在2011年6月宣佈英國演員[[拉塞爾·托維|拉塞爾·托維]]將會參演《新福爾摩斯》的第二季第二集<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s129/sherlock/news/a327636/russell-tovey-to-appear-in-sherlock.html |title=Russell Tovey to appear in 'Sherlock' |first=Morgan |last=Jeffery |date=2011-06-30 |accessdate=2012-04-06 |work=Digital Spy |publisher=Hachette Filipacchi Médias |archive-date=2012-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120716073510/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s129/sherlock/news/a327636/russell-tovey-to-appear-in-sherlock.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。托維對於成為劇中的一角感到相當興奮，並稱與康柏拜區和費里曼拍戲的過程很美妙<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cultbox.co.uk/interviews/exclusives/2341-russell-tovey-sherlock-and-being-human-interview |title=Russell Tovey ('Sherlock' and 'Being Human') interview |first=Will |last=Martin |date=2011-11-01 |accessdate=2012-05-06 |work=Cult Box |archive-date=2013-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103022538/http://www.cultbox.co.uk/interviews/exclusives/2341-russell-tovey-sherlock-and-being-human-interview |dead-url=no }}</ref>。對於亨利這角色，托維表示他不想讓該角只是說話口齒不清，而是雖受困擾但仍成熟可靠的人。為此，編劇馬克·加蒂斯把該角加入了[[幸存者内疚|-{幸}-存者内疚感]]的元素<ref name=commentary/>。值得一提的是，劇組最初打算讓托維的侄子飾演兒時的亨利。然而，由於他年紀過輕的關係，該角色最終還是由另一名兒童演員扮演<ref name=commentary>{{cite video |date=2012 |title=Commentary for "The Hounds of Baskerville" |people=馬克·蓋提斯、史蒂芬·莫弗特、拉塞爾·托維、蘇惟周|medium=Sherlock, Complete Second Series (DVD/Blu-ray) Disc 1 |publisher=2 Entertain}}</ref>。

===劇本創作===
《巴斯克維爾獵犬》是改編自亞瑟·柯南·道爾爵士的《[[巴斯克維爾的獵犬|巴斯克維爾的獵犬]]》。在小說中，福爾摩斯和華生需要到一間別墅查案，由於恐怖的氣氛，該作成為福爾摩斯原著中一部最有名的小說。由於小說的知名度高，編劇馬克．蓋提斯認為他有更大的責任把原著中的恐怖元素注入劇中<ref name=commentary/>。他解釋「我想把劇集變愈恐怖愈好，但這不是鬼屋般的驚嚇，而是不知名政府和[[陰謀論|陰謀論]]這些會使現代人覺得害怕的東西。所以，《巴斯克維爾獵犬》的主題不是可怕的鬼屋，而是黑暗的謠言」<ref name="gat-rt"/>。

此外，福爾摩斯的性情也被改寫。在原著中，福爾摩斯是一個絕對理性的人物，事事會以常理來分析，且不帶任何感情，尤其是遇上不可能的事情時，這情況會變得更為明顯。但在劇中，為使福爾摩斯變得更人性化，蓋提斯刻意把這角色加添了情感<ref name=commentary/>。在這一集中，當福爾摩斯在幻覺下看到獵犬時就怕得不敢相信此事<ref name=sherlockincovered>{{cite video |date=2012 |title=Sherlock Uncovered |people=班奈狄克·康柏拜區、馬丁·費里曼、保羅·麥桂根、史蒂芬·莫弗特|medium=Sherlock, Complete Second Series (DVD/Blu-ray) Disc 2 |publisher=2 Entertain}}</ref>。

一些劇情也被改寫。在《巴斯克維爾的獵犬》，白瑞摩（Barrymore）是男管家，而在劇集中，他成了陸軍研究基地的[[少校|少校]]；摩梯末醫生則由男性變為女性<ref name=commentary/>。另外，在原著的初稿中，本有亨利爵士誤殺摩梯末一幕，但劇組認為後者的離世會使亨利崩潰，故此他們棄用了這劇情<ref name=commentary/>。初稿中，還有亨利爵士之父因私事被殺，劇組則改寫成他因知道法蘭克蘭繼續從事迷幻劑的研究而惹來殺機<ref name=commentary/>。最後一幕也與原著不一，莫里亞蒂在小說中被判入獄；但在本集，他卻被邁克羅夫特從拘留室釋放<ref name=commentary/>。

===拍攝和效果===
[[File:Bush_Inn,_St_Hilary_-_geograph.org.uk_-_273288.jpg|thumb]]的聖希利村。]]

《巴斯克維爾獵犬》在2011年5月正式開鏡，並用了四個星期來拍攝，一些的補鏡則在同年7月和8月完成<ref name=commentary/>。拍攝地點主要在南威爾士。劇組解釋選擇在這兒取景是因為「看起來很英格蘭」，而福爾摩斯和華生到過的旅館是位於[[格拉摩根谷|格拉摩根谷]]的聖希利村<ref name=commentary/>。為了答謝該村落讓出地方拍攝，劇組在製作完畢後向當地捐出了500[[英鎊|英鎊]] <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/need-to-read/2012/01/07/village-pub-to-feature-in-final-episode-of-sherlock-91466-30074939/ |title=Village pub to feature in final episode of Sherlock |date=2012-01-07 |work=Wales Online |publisher=Trinity Mirror |accessdate=2012-01-17 |archive-date=2012-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120115155925/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/need-to-read/2012/01/07/village-pub-to-feature-in-final-episode-of-sherlock-91466-30074939/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

除了南威爾士和達特穆爾外，劇組還在其它地方取景。當中包括[[卡迪夫|卡迪夫]]的威爾士大森林地質公園（Forest Fawr Country Park）、[[倫敦|倫敦]]高爾北街（North Gower Street）185號等和達特穆爾的獵犬谷等<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sherlockology.com/episodes/the-hounds-of-baskerville |title=The Hounds of Baskerville |access-date=2014-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219121211/http://www.sherlockology.com/episodes/the-hounds-of-baskerville |archive-date=2014-02-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。至於劇中所謂的研究所其實是鄰近[[梅瑟蒂德菲爾|梅瑟蒂德菲爾]]的一間芯片加工工廠<ref name=commentary/>。

另一方面，本劇出現過不少動物，比如一隻發光的兔子和那頭獵犬。為了使獵犬在鏡頭前顯得更為真實，但又要避免被觀眾投訴，劇組最終採用電腦效果繪出牠而非在真的狗上加工<ref name="indy">{{cite news |first=Gerard |last=Gilbert |title=The case of the amazing reinvention: On set with the stars of TV’s Sherlock |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/features/the-case-of-the-amazing-reinvention-on-set-with-the-stars-of-tvs-sherlock-6274034.html |work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |publisher=Independent Print Limited |date=2011-12-09 |accessdate=2012-01-09 |archive-date=2013-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216201851/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/features/the-case-of-the-amazing-reinvention-on-set-with-the-stars-of-tvs-sherlock-6274034.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但發光兔子卻不是由電腦造出來的，而是由劇組人員在一頭真的白兔表面添上可於[[水母|水母]]找到的[[綠色熒光蛋白|綠色熒光蛋白]] <ref name=commentary/>。

==回響==
《巴斯克維爾獵犬》在2012年11月8日在[[BBC_One|BBC One]]和[[BBC_HD|BBC HD]]首播。當晚的初步調查指，全英共有816萬通過電視收看此節目，[[收視率|收視率]]達29%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2012/jan/09/dancing-on-ice-sherlock |title=Dancing on Ice left clueless by Sherlock |first=John |last=Plunkett |date=2012-01-09 |accessdate=2012-05-05 |work=[[衛報|The Guardian]] |publisher=Guardian Media Group |archive-date=2012-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120113074514/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2012/jan/09/dancing-on-ice-sherlock |dead-url=no }}</ref>。儘管相比[[貝爾戈維亞醜聞|上一集]]，這集的收看人數減少了40萬人，但它還是同一時段中最多人收看的電視節目。而在其後發佈的最終收視報告更指有1266萬觀眾觀看此劇，成為這星期內收視亞軍<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.barb.co.uk/viewing/weekly-top-10?_s=4 |title=Weekly Top 10 Programmes (select BBC1 and w/e 8 January 2011) |accessdate=2012-05-05 |publisher=Broadcasters' Audience Research Board |archive-date=2012-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121217063204/http://www.barb.co.uk/viewing/weekly-top-10?_s=4 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.barb.co.uk/viewing/weekly-top-30?_s=4 |title=Weekly Top 30 Programmes (select w/e 8 January 2012) |accessdate=2012-05-05 |publisher=Broadcasters' Audience Research Board |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064021/http://barb.co.uk/viewing/weekly-top-30?_s=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。BBC Three亦在一星期後重播此劇，也有70萬人收看<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.barb.co.uk/viewing/weekly-top-10?_s=4 |title=Weekly Top 10 Programmes (select BBC3 and w/e 15 January 2011) |accessdate=2012-05-07 |publisher=Broadcasters' Audience Research Board |archive-date=2012-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121217063204/http://www.barb.co.uk/viewing/weekly-top-10?_s=4 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。另外，直至到同年5月，還有160萬人通過[[BBC_iPlayer|BBC iPlayer]] 看這一集，是2012年上半年收看人數第三高的節目<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/bbc/9297689/Sherlock-episode-with-naked-Lara-Pulver-most-watched-show-on-BBC-iPlayer.html|title=Sherlock episode with naked Lara Pulver most watched show on BBC iPlayer|work=[[每日電訊報|The Daily Telegraph]]|date=2012-05-29|accessdate=2012-06-08|archive-date=2017-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170909213843/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/bbc/9297689/Sherlock-episode-with-naked-Lara-Pulver-most-watched-show-on-BBC-iPlayer.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

考慮到這集一些鏡頭具「溫和的武力成份」，[[英國電影分級委員會|英國電影分級委員會]]把這集列為12級，即適合12歲以上的觀眾收看<ref>{{cite web |title=SHERLOCK - THE HOUNDS OF BASKERVILLE|url=http://www.bbfc.co.uk/AVV286085/ |work=British Board of Film Classification |date=2011-12-20|accessdate=2012-01-08}}</ref>。此外，本集已被收藏在《新福爾摩斯》第二季的影碟中，並以[[DVD|DVD]]和[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]的形式在2012年1月23日發售<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbcshop.com/drama+arts/sherlock-series-2-dvd/invt/bbcdvd3494/ |title=Sherlock: Series 2 (DVD) |accessdate=2012-04-07 |work=BBC Shop |publisher=BBC Online |archive-date=2012-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120120010859/http://www.bbcshop.com/drama+arts/sherlock-series-2-blu-ray/invt/bbcbd0167 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbcshop.com/drama+arts/sherlock-series-2-blu-ray/invt/bbcbd0167/ |title=Sherlock: Series 2 (Blu-ray) |accessdate=2012-05-07 |work=BBC Shop |publisher=BBC Online |archive-date=2012-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120120010859/http://www.bbcshop.com/drama+arts/sherlock-series-2-blu-ray/invt/bbcbd0167 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===評價===
《巴斯克維爾獵犬》取得大量的好評。《[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]》在5顆星為滿分下給了4星<ref name=" Davies "/>。主筆戴維絲以「很棒」來形容此集，又認為福爾摩斯在片中變得更人性化﹔對於事主被迷幻藥加害，以致誤認為其父被獵犬所殺的劇情，戴維絲感到相當驚喜<ref name=" Davies ">{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/8998621/Sherlock-The-Hounds-of-Baskerville-BBC-One-review.html |title=Sherlock: The Hounds of Baskerville, BBC One, review |first=Serena |last=Davies |date=2012-01-08 |accessdate=2012-05-09 |work=[[每日電訊報|The Daily Telegraph]] |publisher=Telegraph Media Group |archive-date=2013-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216150916/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/8998621/Sherlock-The-Hounds-of-Baskerville-BBC-One-review.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。多媒體和評論網站TV Fanatic在5星為滿分下給了3星，主編保羅稱這集的[[美術指導|美術指導]]令人讚不絕口，細節也做得很好<ref name="Fanatic"/>。

《[[衞報|衞報]]》的山姆·沃拉斯頓也喜歡這集。他說劇情有二十一世紀的味道，福爾摩斯也一如大家所望的聰明機智，而氣氛也讓人毛骨悚然<ref>{{cite news |first=Sam |last=Wollaston |title=TV review: Borgen; Sherlock |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/2012/jan/07/tv-review-borgen-sherlock |date=2012-01-08 |work=[[衛報|The Guardian]] |publisher=Guardian Media Group |accessdate=2012-01-08 |archive-date=2013-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130109035947/http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/2012/jan/07/tv-review-borgen-sherlock |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[廣播時報|廣播時報]]》的大衛·畢查在對比[[貝爾戈維亞醜聞|上集]]的開場後，大讚本集善用令人緊張不安的攝影手法，加上懸疑和偏執，使人不寒而慄<ref>{{cite web |first=David |last=Butcher |title=Sherlock Series 2 - 2. The Hounds of Baskerville |url=http://www.radiotimes.com/episode/n6g74/sherlock--series-2---2-the-hounds-of-baskerville |work=[[廣播時報|Radio Times]] |publisher=BBC Magazines |accessdate=2012-01-08 |archive-date=2014-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209001211/http://www.radiotimes.com/episode/n6g74/sherlock--series-2---2-the-hounds-of-baskerville |dead-url=no }}</ref>。免費報章《都會報》的基斯杜化評此集完美的把「霧、不祥的沼澤、現代和節奏明快的驚悚片」結合起來，加上康柏拜區出眾的演技，使得看《新福爾摩斯》的一個半小時過得特別快<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metro.co.uk/tv/reviews/886766-sherlock-showed-how-the-remake-should-be-done |title=Sherlock showed how the remake should be done |first=Christopher |last=Hootan |date=2012-01-08|accessdate=2012-05-10|work=Metro |publisher=Associated Newspapers}}</ref>。

獨立出版社《Den of Geek》的路易莎·梅勒稱讚這集的恐怖環節處理得非常好，並將此歸功於負責配音的大衞·阿諾德和馬克爾·派斯<ref name=denofgeek>{{cite web |url=http://www.denofgeek.com/television/1196151/sherlock_series_2_episode_2_the_hounds_of_baskerville_review.html |title=Sherlock series 2 episode 2: The Hounds of Baskerville review |first=Louisa |last=Mellor |date=2012-01-08 |accessdate=2012-05-09 |work=Den of Geek |archive-date=2012-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120414075541/http://www.denofgeek.com/television/1196151/sherlock_series_2_episode_2_the_hounds_of_baskerville_review.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同時，她又大讚編劇馬克·加蒂斯對劇情的編排，特別是福爾摩斯使用記憶宮殿的那一幕<ref name=denofgeek/>。另一方面，她也嘉許托維和費里曼精湛的演出。總結道，她以劇的一句「這一案，太棒了，謝謝」來形容本集<ref name=denofgeek/>。[[IGN|IGN]]的克里斯·提莉在10分中給了7分，但認為這集的主要劇情不足以演繹90分鐘，劇集要以無關痛痒的情節和效果來支撐，讓人看得失去耐性<ref name="IGN">{{cite web |url=http://uk.tv.ign.com/articles/121/1216097p1.html |title=Sherlock: "The Hounds of Baskerville" Review |first=Chris |last=Tilly |date=2012-01-09 |accessdate=2012-05-09 |work=[[IGN|IGN]] |publisher=News Corporation |archive-date=2012-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120129063248/http://uk.tv.ign.com/articles/121/1216097p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不過，她還是對劇中三位主角的演出表示欣賞<ref name="IGN"/>。

CultBox的大衛·劉易斯評論道，這集是一輯「關於化學戰爭、掩蓋和巨型[[犬科|犬科]]，又頗為直接的恐怖片」<ref name=" David ">{{cite web |url=http://www.cultbox.co.uk/reviews/episodes/2706-sherlock-the-hounds-of-baskerville-review |title='Sherlock': 'The Hounds of Baskerville' review |first=David |last=Lewis |date=2012-01-08 |accessdate=2012-05-09 |work=CultBox |archive-date=2013-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103022827/http://www.cultbox.co.uk/reviews/episodes/2706-sherlock-the-hounds-of-baskerville-review |dead-url=no }}</ref>。對於那頭獵犬的造型，劉易斯則直言「這一如過去各福爾摩斯電影和電視劇般的差勁」<ref name=" David "/>。摩根．傑弗里在《Digital Spy》則給了剛剛相反的意見，他認為那頭獵犬的像真度很高，使他印象深刻，又覺得這集既有趣又可怕<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s129/sherlock/recaps/a358622/sherlock-the-hounds-of-baskerville-recap.html |title='Sherlock': 'The Hounds of Baskerville' recap |first=Morgan |last=Jeffery |date=2012-01-08 |accessdate=2012-05-09 |work=Digital Spy |publisher=Hachette Filipacchi Médias |archive-date=2014-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140113111848/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s129/sherlock/recaps/a358622/sherlock-the-hounds-of-baskerville-recap.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

然而，並非所有評價人也滿意這集。WhatCulture的湯·雷恩在5星為滿分下只給了本集2星半<ref name="Tom">{{cite web |url=http://whatculture.com/tv/tv-review-sherlock-2-2-the-hounds-of-baskerville.php |title=TV Review: SHERLOCK 2.2, 'The Hounds of Baskerville' |first=Tom |last=Ryan |date=2012-01-10 |accessdate=2012-05-10 |publisher=WhatCulture |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120221095811/http://whatculture.com/tv/tv-review-sherlock-2-2-the-hounds-of-baskerville.php |archivedate=2012-02-21 }}</ref>。他說考慮到原著的著名度和本電視劇的成功度，這集無疑是平庸的<ref name="Tom"/>。《衛報》的斯圖亞特也有同感，他認為這集沒有預期般好看，又指福爾摩斯和華生各為其政，失去了過去的化學反應。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/tvandradioblog/2012/jan/09/sherlock-double-act |title=Sherlock: it's all about the double act |first=Stuart |last=Heritage |date=2012-01-09 |accessdate=2012-05-10 |work=[[衛報|The Guardian]] |publisher=Guardian Media Group |archive-date=2012-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120112082458/http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/tvandradioblog/2012/jan/09/sherlock-double-act |dead-url=no }}</ref>約翰·特蒂在娛樂報紙《[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]》更是大力加鞭，他給了本集C-的低分，批評這集莫不相干的枝節太多、摩梯末醫生沒有存在的必要以及結局脫離現實，更重要的是法蘭克蘭行徑特出，「像是把奸角二字寫在額頭上」，總的來說，這集實在讓人大失所望<ref name=" The A.V. Club "/>。雖然如此，特蒂還是對托維的演出很欣賞<ref name=" The A.V. Club "/>。

